enterprise.name: Tumorotek
enterprise.description: Web application that manages biological samples utilized by hospitals across France.
enterprise.subtitle: This intricate application enables users to oversee patient information, sample data, byproducts, and the associated cryogenic storage units. It facilitates tracking the location of each sample within the storage units, and provides an administrative panel for enhanced control and monitoring.

enterprise.name: Biomedicine Agency
enterprise.description: Web application that manages bone marrow donors and recipients, ensuring seamless coordination in the donation process.
enterprise.subtitle: This application ensures efficient management of bone marrow donors and recipients, promoting seamless coordination throughout the donation process. Utilizing Java, Spring, TypeScript, and Angular, it offers a robust solution for the biomedical domain.

enterprise.name: Gatsbi
enterprise.subtitle: Gatsby introduces a contextual dimension to Tumorotek, allowing for the definition and utilization of specific contexts within Tumorotek
